flowchart TD
  A[Trigger: Daily batch job to initiate logistics optimization process.]
  A --> N1[Stream: DDM/Crawlers - Extract carrier data and shipment plans from SAP S/4HANA.]
  N1 --> N2[Cortex: Cortex Auto Forecast - Analyze carrier data and shipment plans to optimize TMS settings.]
  N2 --> N3[Cortex: UI Screens - Generate logistics performance reports and dashboards.]
  N3 --> N4[Stream: STREAMS - Integrate telematics data for real-time fleet tracking and optimization.]
  N4 --> N5[PB: Remote Functions - Update TMS settings and EDI connections based on analysis.]
  N5 --> N6[PB: Cortex Monitoring - Review and monitor the effectiveness of the new configurations.]
  N6 --> N7{Decision: Optimize transportation configuration, carrier management, logistics analytics, and fleet telematics.}
  N6 --> Z1[Outcome: Reduced COGS, prevented stockouts, improved OTIF through real-time, cross-system decisions.]
  N7 -->|Carrier data is incomplete or outdated.| B1[Trigger manual review and update process.]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Manual intervention to correct data issues.]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N7 -->|Telematics data integration fails.| B2[Notify operations team to investigate and resolve.]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: Resolved data integration issues and resumed optimization.]
  O2 --> End[End]
  N7 -->|Generated reports do not meet actiona...| B3[Adjust report definitions and regenerate.]
  B3 --> O3[Outcome: Improved report actionability and utility.]
  O3 --> End[End]
  Z1 --> End[End]